We operate across Hampshire, Dorset, Berkshire, Oxfordshire and other neighbouring counties, providing:
- support for people living in their own homes or in shared housing
- support for people to find and maintain suitable accommodation
- positive behaviour support, including specialist behaviour consultancy and training
- outreach and opportunities to participate in community activities

Our services are funded through contracts placed by local authorities. Some people have Personal Budgets and can purchase their own support.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b9edca54-77d7-49b0-8b11-2100149c4f10.png', TRUE, 'Medium-sized company', 1, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-09T00:00:00+00:00', 'b9edca54-77d7-49b0-8b11-2100149c4f10') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Pacific Summit Energy', 'Pacific Summit Energy LLC', 'https://pacificsummitenergy.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/pacific-summit-energy', 'Pacific Summit Energy LLC (PSE) is a North American energy marketing and trading company established in 2004 as a subsidiary of Sumitomo Corporation. Headquartered in Irvine, California, PSE operates across key U.S. locations, including California, Texas, and Virginia, with a workforce of approximately 80-104 employees. The company reported annual revenue of about $26 million in 2025 and has expanded its presence internationally, including a UK establishment opened in July 2025.

PSE specializes in energy trading and supply solutions, focusing on natural gas, LNG, electric power, and environmental products. Its offerings include fixed and index price trading for natural gas, global LNG operations, and comprehensive electric power services. The company is committed to supporting Sumitomo''s carbon neutrality goal by 2050 through sustainable practices and emphasizes building long-term partnerships to address energy challenges. PSE serves over 600 counterparties, including wholesale trading companies and utilities, contributing to the dynamic energy market.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b27d58fb-049f-4391-9dcd-5c1c4e3f4da1.png', TRUE, 'Medium-sized company', NULL, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-16T00:00:00+00:00', 'b27d58fb-049f-4391-9dcd-5c1c4e3f4da1') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Paddington Robotics', 'Paddington Robotics', 'https://paddington-robotics.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/paddington-robotics', 'Paddington Robotics is a UK-based startup founded in 2024, located in London. The company specializes in AI-driven robotics and automation solutions for various industries, including manufacturing, healthcare, logistics, and general-purpose applications like supermarkets. Led by Dr. Zehan Wang, a former Twitter AI executive, Paddington Robotics aims to advance robotics through innovative systems that address real-world challenges.

The company develops robotic systems that integrate AI, software, hardware, and robotics for practical use. Their focus includes general-purpose robotics powered by embodied AI, which allows systems to learn and adapt in diverse environments. Paddington Robotics emphasizes creating tailored solutions to enhance productivity and efficiency while addressing hardware standardization and data challenges. The company values innovation, quality, and collaboration, with a vision to make automation accessible for businesses of all sizes.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 4, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/bb0571ce-38d8-4100-8d86-cca23418239f.png', TRUE, 'Small company', NULL, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-16T00:00:00+00:00', 'bb0571ce-38d8-4100-8d86-cca23418239f') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Pear Bio', 'Pear Bio', 'https://www.pearbio.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/pear-bio/', 'Pear Bio is a computational biology and AI-enabled biotech company founded in 2017, with headquarters in London, UK, and Boston/Natick, Massachusetts. The company focuses on developing functional precision medicine platforms aimed at optimizing cancer treatment and drug discovery. Led by founder and CEO Duleek Ranatunga, Pear Bio integrates tissue engineering, confocal microscopy, and computer vision into a patient stratification tool that analyzes the human tumor microenvironment.

The company offers personalized testing services to predict effective therapies for individual patients, maintains a drug discovery pipeline targeting novel druggable options, and provides clinical trial support to match patients with experimental drugs. Pear Bio''s technology is particularly focused on biomarker-negative cancers, including triple-negative breast cancer, and is expanding its clinical trials in breast and kidney cancer. With a team of 32 and recent funding of $15 million in Series A, Pear Bio is actively involved in advancing cancer treatment solutions.', NULL, 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/1190.png', TRUE, 'Small company', NULL, NULL, FALSE, '2026-03-06T00:00:00+00:00', '1190') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Peavey Electronics', 'Peavey Electronics LTD', 'https://peavey.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/peaveyelectronics', 'Peavey Electronics Corporation, founded in 1965 by Hartley Peavey in Meridian, Mississippi, is a leading manufacturer and supplier of musical instruments, amplifiers, and professional audio systems. The company has grown significantly, distributing over 2,000 products to more than 130 countries. Peavey emphasizes innovation, quality, and affordability, adhering to the founder''s philosophy of providing top-notch gear at fair prices.

Peavey produces a diverse range of products, including guitars, electronic keyboards, and high-power amplifiers. Notable innovations include the MediaMatrix system, a pioneering audio networking solution, and advancements in class-D power amplifier technology. The company has earned numerous awards for its contributions to the industry and holds over 180 patents worldwide. Peavey also operates its own advertising agency and maintains in-house production for many components, ensuring a high level of quality and reliability in its offerings.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/786737f3-f4dc-4ed1-878b-b12a5f52972a.png', TRUE, 'Medium-sized company', NULL, NULL, FALSE, '2026-02-23T00:00:00+00:00', '786737f3-f4dc-4ed1-878b-b12a5f52972a') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Perfumer H', 'Lyn Michel LTD', 'https://www.perfumerh.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/perfumer-h', 'Perfumer H is a British fragrance house founded in 2015 by Lyn Harris, a classically trained perfumer based in London. The brand focuses on the artisanal craft of perfume-making, emphasizing natural ingredients and sensory experiences. With six stores globally, including a flagship location in Marylebone, Perfumer H offers a range of products that include unique Eau de Parfum collections, bespoke fragrances, handblown glass candles, traditional incense, and pantry items.

Lyn Harris, recognized as England''s first trained female perfumer, has a deep connection to scent, influenced by her childhood in the Scottish Highlands. She trained in Grasse, France, and collaborates with the family-owned fragrance manufacturer Robertet. Perfumer H is committed to ethical sourcing and sustainability, partnering with global communities and acclaimed creatives to ensure quality and artistry in every product. The brand''s visual identity, crafted by Studio Frith, reflects a connection to nature and meticulous attention to detail.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/36b94ae7-635c-4e86-9f24-f7eced017392.png', TRUE, 'Small company', NULL, NULL, FALSE, '2026-02-23T00:00:00+00:00', '36b94ae7-635c-4e86-9f24-f7eced017392') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Pexapark', 'Pexapark UK Ltd', 'https://pexapark.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/pexapark', 'Pexapark is an enterprise software and advisory company founded in 2017, focusing on renewable energy, particularly power purchase agreements (PPAs) and risk management. The company has supported over 30GW of renewable PPA transactions across Europe and the United States. Pexapark aims to accelerate the energy transition toward net zero by creating an efficient renewable energy market.

The company offers a comprehensive software platform for managing renewable energy investments, including tools for PPA pricing, deal execution, portfolio monitoring, and risk analytics. Pexapark also provides advisory services to assist with PPA transactions, strategy development, and market intelligence. Their offerings include daily PPA reference prices, educational resources, and market trend updates. With a team of over 100 employees, Pexapark is dedicated to digitizing the route to market for renewables, making it easier for energy players to execute deals and manage risks effectively.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/8c7d42ee-5589-4953-b425-af36a52d73a0.png', TRUE, 'Medium-sized company', NULL, NULL, FALSE, '2026-02-27T00:00:00+00:00', '8c7d42ee-5589-4953-b425-af36a52d73a0') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Plasma', 'Plasma Labs UK Limited', 'https://www.plasma.to', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/plasmafdn', 'Plasma is a Layer 1 blockchain focused on stablecoin transactions, designed for efficient global money movement. It offers sub-second settlement times and low or zero fees, making it ideal for cross-border payments and everyday financial services. The platform supports thousands of transactions per second and is built on a modular Ethereum execution client, ensuring robust security and performance.

Key offerings include instant stablecoin payments, a neobank app called Plasma One for managing digital dollars, and a compliance infrastructure that meets regulatory standards. Plasma also provides tools for smart accounts and security, enabling features like multisig wallets and asset management. The ecosystem supports various integrations with DeFi platforms, payment protocols, and analytics tools, targeting a wide range of users from remittance providers to corporate treasuries.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 1, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e7854a6e-cb73-49df-9d10-fd9b8ded9cc4.png', TRUE, 'Small company', NULL, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-19T00:00:00+00:00', 'e7854a6e-cb73-49df-9d10-fd9b8ded9cc4') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Plysolene', 'Plysolene Limited', 'https://plysolene.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/plysolenelimited', 'Plysolene has been extruding thermoplastic sheet for over 50 years, supplying bespoke sheet to a wide range of industries including point of sale display, packaging, construction & insulation.

Our flexibility ensures lead times are kept to an absolute minimum, which enables customers to meet tight deadlines and reduce costs.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/537cff51-8a65-4c83-9727-c4a666dd5411.png', TRUE, 'Small company', NULL, NULL, FALSE, '2026-03-06T00:00:00+00:00', '537cff51-8a65-4c83-9727-c4a666dd5411') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Polunin Capital Partners', 'Polunin Capital Partners Limited', 'https://polunin.co.uk/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/polunincapitalpartnerslimited', 'Founded in 2001, Polunin is an employee-owned value specialist managing c. $7.5bln in International and Emerging Markets equity portfolios on behalf of an  exclusively institutional client base.

We believe that markets are inherently cyclical and oscillate consistently around a secular trend driven by predictable human behaviour. Understanding cycles results in a knowledge-advantage vis-à-vis peers. Whilst we do not pretend to know the future, we do aim to tilt the odds of reaping asymmetric returns in our favour


Exploiting the profit potential of market cycles requires a disciplined investment approach. We combine proprietary valuation metrics that filter out market noise with an ability to be contrarian when the payoff for betting against consensus is overwhelmingly in our favour.

We believe that our distinctive investment process typically results in return and portfolio characteristics that offer significant diversification benefits.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/21a32068-0668-4672-b3fa-429804cfe5ba.png', TRUE, 'Small company', NULL, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-19T00:00:00+00:00', '21a32068-0668-4672-b3fa-429804cfe5ba') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Port.io', 'Port IO UK Limited', 'https://www.port.io', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/getport', 'Port.io is an internal developer portal platform founded in 2022, with headquarters in Tel Aviv and additional offices in Austin and Boston. The company focuses on enabling engineering teams to create self-service experiences and automate workflows, providing a unified view of the software development lifecycle (SDLC). With around 175 employees, Port.io offers tools for platform engineering and DevOps, including a Context Lake for data consolidation, a software catalog for ecosystem modeling, and AI agents to streamline operations.

The platform emphasizes dynamic modeling to enhance self-service capabilities and support multi-domain engineering at scale. It helps managers track key metrics such as developer productivity and software quality while minimizing bottlenecks for developers. Port.io has raised $60 million in funding, including a recent $35 million Series B round, and is recognized for its innovative approach in the internal developer portal space. The company promotes a hybrid work model and has a diverse team across various roles.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/3961f25c-1f3c-4e42-9aff-47735b583cf4.png', TRUE, 'Large company', NULL, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-12T00:00:00+00:00', '3961f25c-1f3c-4e42-9aff-47735b583cf4') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('QUBIS', 'QUBIS Limited', 'https://www.qubis.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/qubis-ltd', 'QUBIS Ltd was formed in 1984 by Queen''s University Belfast in order to commercialize the University''s research and development activities through the formulation of spin-out businesses. The University through QUBIS Ltd, takes an equity holding in a new spin-out venture in return for an investment of cash and/or Intellectual Property. Our major aim is to ‘pull through'' appropriate R&D from the laboratory into the commercial market place.

QUBIS Ltd proactively seeks to identify and evaluate commercially exploitable research and resources from Queen''s University. Management and partners, who have appropriate skills and access to the market place, are then sought. All new ventures are market led and only those with strong feedback from the market place are actually undertaken. Our experience has shown that the support of a private or trade investor, particularly one who brings access to markets, eg. having an established distribution system or presence in a relevant market, is especially desirable.

The immediate objective of QUBIS Ltd as a holding company, is to establish an ongoing stream of dividend, or other income, from its investments. We are patient investors and all of our investments are undertaken for the medium to long term, we do not look for an early exit.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/66e20762-fa0a-4e1f-b2aa-0e249aa72a35.png', TRUE, 'Small company', NULL, NULL, FALSE, '2026-03-04T00:00:00+00:00', '66e20762-fa0a-4e1f-b2aa-0e249aa72a35') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Radiant', 'Ori Industries 1 Ltd', 'https://radiant.co/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/radiant-co/', 'Radiant Nuclear, also known as Radiant Industries, Inc., is a clean energy startup founded in 2020 by former SpaceX engineers Doug Bernauer and Bob Urberger. Headquartered in El Segundo, California, with a manufacturing base in Oak Ridge, Tennessee, the company focuses on developing portable nuclear microreactors as zero-emission alternatives to diesel generators. Their flagship product, the Kaleidos Microreactor, is designed to provide reliable power for off-grid and resilient applications.

The Kaleidos Microreactor is a 1 MW electric unit that fits in a standard shipping container, making it easy to transport. It operates without the need for on-site water and features a 20-year lifespan with refueling every five years. The microreactor is suitable for various applications, including remote villages, hospitals, military bases, and AI data centers. Radiant Nuclear aims to mass-produce these units, with testing planned for 2026 and initial deployments expected in 2028. The company is committed to replacing diesel generators globally with clean, portable nuclear power.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 9, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/21d0ed26-b0dd-4cb7-853e-a16915ca5f44.png', TRUE, 'Small company', NULL, NULL, FALSE, '2019-06-21T00:00:00+00:00', '21d0ed26-b0dd-4cb7-853e-a16915ca5f44') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Reward', 'Sports Loyalty Card Limited t/a Reward', 'https://rewardinsight.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/reward', 'Reward Insight is a UK-based technology company founded in 2001, focused on customer engagement, banking loyalty programs, and commerce media solutions. Headquartered in London, the company utilizes AI-driven analytics from transaction data to provide personalized rewards and insights. Reward Insight operates a cloud-based API platform that transforms everyday spending into rewarding experiences, serving over 15 markets across Europe, the Middle East, and Asia.

The company offers a range of services, including card-linked rewards that enable automatic cashback through banking apps, personalized offers using behavioral intelligence, and intelligence products for customer understanding. Reward Insight partners with major banks and retailers, including NatWest Group, Barclays, and McDonald’s, reaching over 150 million customers globally. With a mission to align banks, retailers, and consumers for mutual value, Reward Insight has delivered over $2 billion in cashback rewards and aims to reach $4 billion by 2030.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 10, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/c21f9dcf-c233-492a-9b85-c05abdf0a16e.png', TRUE, 'Large company', 1, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-19T00:00:00+00:00', 'c21f9dcf-c233-492a-9b85-c05abdf0a16e') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Rheinmetall', 'Rheinmetall Weapon Munitions UK Limited', 'https://www.rheinmetall.com/en', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/rheinmetall', 'Rheinmetall AG is a prominent integrated technology group based in Düsseldorf, Germany, with a rich history dating back to 1889. Originally established to produce munitions for the German Empire, it has evolved into the largest German and fifth-largest European arms manufacturer. The company specializes in a wide range of defense and civilian products, including armored fighting vehicles, munitions, and integrated systems for security and mobility.

Rheinmetall operates globally, with facilities in the U.S., India, and Germany. Its U.S. subsidiary, American Rheinmetall, focuses on delivering defense products tailored for the military. The company is committed to engineering excellence and innovation, serving both defense and civilian sectors while maintaining a strong emphasis on supporting warfighters and enhancing security capabilities.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/18c6e21d-400c-4757-9507-f74a95dfa357.png', TRUE, 'Very large company', NULL, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-09T00:00:00+00:00', '18c6e21d-400c-4757-9507-f74a95dfa357') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Ride Therapeutics', 'Ride Therapeutics Limited', 'https://ridetherapeutics.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ride-therapeutics/', 'Ride Therapeutics is a recently formed transatlantic biotechnology company with the mission of unlocking the full potential of mRNA & gene editing therapeutics through targeted & tunable delivery of these modalities. Founded by world-leading scientists from Harvard University & the University of Cambridge, Ride’s unique technology platform provides an entirely new approach to solving the delivery challenge at the molecular level. Powered by micro- and nano-engineering coupled to advanced data science, Ride is building the capability to deliver any molecular cargo, to any cell type, with a tunable release profile.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/2ddd4862-44be-44be-bc62-2dd3d9252261.png', TRUE, NULL, NULL, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-11T00:00:00+00:00', '2ddd4862-44be-44be-bc62-2dd3d9252261') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('SDG Group', 'SDG GROUP UK&I LTD', 'https://www.sdggroup.com/en-gb/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sdg-group', 'SDG Group is a global consulting firm with over 30 years of experience in Data, Analytics, and AI solutions. The company focuses on empowering organizations through innovative, data-driven strategies and a technology-agnostic approach. With a team of more than 2,500 employees, SDG Group serves over 700 customers worldwide, delivering insights that go beyond traditional analytics.

The firm offers a range of services, including Data Strategy & Governance, Analytics Excellence, and Artificial Intelligence. SDG Group collaborates with clients to create tailored solutions that enhance operations and decision-making. Their expertise spans various industries, including pharmaceuticals, water management, retail, and energy. The company also provides proprietary frameworks and solution accelerators, such as predictive modeling tools and platform-agnostic data pipelines, to support clients in achieving their business goals.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 7, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/137802bd-0a9b-44aa-afc5-ca39f5f4f067.png', TRUE, 'Very large company', NULL, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-19T00:00:00+00:00', '137802bd-0a9b-44aa-afc5-ca39f5f4f067') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Sensata Technologies', 'Sensata Technologies Intermediate UK Limited', 'https://www.sensata.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sensata-technologies', 'Sensata Technologies is a global industrial technology company that specializes in developing sensors and sensor-based solutions for mission-critical applications. With over 100 years of experience, the company focuses on creating customized, sensor-rich products that address complex engineering challenges across various industries. Sensata is recognized for its strengths in electrification and autonomy, catering to growing demands in sectors such as HVAC, water management, and aerospace.

The company''s core offerings include a range of sensors designed for electrification, autonomy, HVAC, water management, and aerospace applications. These products provide valuable insights and support efficiency and safety in industrial automation and sustainable technologies. Sensata serves key markets, including automotive and mobility, where it is a leading supplier, as well as industrial applications and aerospace, leveraging its scale to meet diverse customer needs.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 3, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/02d5bd71-34c7-48fb-9232-15c5a02e01f6.png', TRUE, 'Very large company', NULL, NULL, FALSE, NULL, '02d5bd71-34c7-48fb-9232-15c5a02e01f6') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Shepper', 'Shepper Limited', 'https://shepper.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/shepper', 'Shepper is a UK-based data analysis and collection company founded in 2016, headquartered in London. The company specializes in providing real-time, on-demand insights for businesses through a network of over 300,000 local data collectors, known as "Shepherds," across the UK and Ireland. Shepper utilizes AI technology and a digital platform to deliver customized tasks and questionnaires, ensuring data quality and rapid delivery via client-specific dashboards.

The company offers a range of services, including mystery shopping, auditing, brand solutions, and field marketing. These services help businesses optimize customer experience, monitor product availability, and ensure compliance with promotional standards. Shepper''s agile and cost-effective solutions support various sectors, including retail, consumer goods, and media, and are designed to facilitate data-driven decision-making. With a growing user community and a focus on partnerships with leading brands, Shepper continues to expand its impact in the advertising, marketing, and data collection industries.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/f7f19568-fef8-4b89-ae0e-b0f19061b35b.png', TRUE, 'Small company', NULL, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-17T00:00:00+00:00', 'f7f19568-fef8-4b89-ae0e-b0f19061b35b') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Sid Lee Sport', 'Sid Lee Sport Limited', 'https://www.sidleesport.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/sid-lee-sport', 'Sid Lee Sport is the global sports practice of Sid Lee, a creative agency that specializes in integrated sports marketing services. With headquarters in London and additional offices in Los Angeles, Montreal, New York, and Toronto, the agency combines creativity, sponsorship expertise, and operational delivery to enhance sports marketing for sponsors, rights holders, and sports brands.

Launched after Sid Lee''s merger with Infrared in 2021, Sid Lee Sport aims to challenge traditional sports marketing norms. The agency offers a range of services, including sponsorship negotiation and activation, creative campaign development, event execution, and effectiveness measurement. Their proprietary Sid Lee Fame Cycle framework helps create memorable brand interactions. The agency has collaborated with notable clients such as Tommy Hilfiger, Visa, UEFA, OPPO, and Lidl, showcasing its ability to deliver impactful and engaging marketing solutions in the sports sector.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/7bf343e9-b261-4d0c-83e1-eff109f2929f.png', TRUE, 'Small company', NULL, NULL, FALSE, '2026-03-04T00:00:00+00:00', '7bf343e9-b261-4d0c-83e1-eff109f2929f') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Siemens', 'Siemens Holdings plc (including Siemens plc)', 'https://www.siemens.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/siemens', 'Siemens AG is a German multinational conglomerate based in Munich, founded in 1847. The company has a rich history in electrical engineering and has evolved into a global technology leader operating in over 200 countries. Siemens focuses on energy technology, manufacturing, and innovation across various sectors, including healthcare, infrastructure, and industrial applications.

Siemens offers a wide range of products and services. In energy and power, it provides equipment for power generation and transmission, including gas turbines and energy management systems. The transportation and infrastructure segment includes electric railways and mass transit systems. In medical engineering, Siemens develops diagnostic imaging systems and hearing aids. The company also produces industrial and electrical equipment, such as dynamos, telecommunication systems, and HVAC controls. Siemens is recognized for its commitment to research and development, holding a significant number of patents and continuously innovating in technology.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/710ba99a-7537-455f-a713-671de9534e9a.png', TRUE, 'Very large company', 40, NULL, FALSE, NULL, '710ba99a-7537-455f-a713-671de9534e9a') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Smarsh', 'Smarsh Software UK Ltd', 'https://www.smarsh.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/smarsh', 'Smarsh is a prominent provider of cloud-native, AI-powered solutions for digital communications governance and archiving. Founded in 2001 by Stephen Marsh, the company has evolved from an email archiving service to a comprehensive platform that supports over 100 communication channels, managing billions of messages each month. Headquartered in Portland, Oregon, Smarsh reported $111.4 million in annual revenue in 2024 and employs around 1,348 people globally.

Smarsh offers a range of AI-enabled solutions that include capturing, retaining, and analyzing communications data to help regulated organizations manage compliance risks. Their services encompass secure archiving, efficient search and review tools, and AI-powered risk detection. The company serves a diverse client base, including top global banks, brokerage firms, insurers, and government agencies, focusing on delivering trusted compliance solutions for regulated industries. Recognized as a leader in its field, Smarsh continues to innovate in cloud, AI, and regulatory technology.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 6, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ebaf31d0-f6ad-4fc5-817c-989769b44f82.png', TRUE, 'Very large company', NULL, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-19T00:00:00+00:00', 'ebaf31d0-f6ad-4fc5-817c-989769b44f82') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Soho Square Capital', 'Soho Square Advisory Services Ltd', 'https://www.soho-sq.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/soho-square-capital', 'Soho Square Capital LLP is a London-based investment firm that specializes in providing structured capital solutions to small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) in the UK and Europe. Founded in 2012, the firm focuses on empowering business leaders to achieve their long-term goals while minimizing equity dilution. Soho Square has completed over 65 investments, typically targeting amounts between £15-40 million.

The firm offers flexible financing options tailored to the unique needs of each business. These solutions are designed for various scenarios, including ownership transitions, growth funding, and debt refinancing. By combining capital with operational expertise, Soho Square acts as a trusted partner to entrepreneurs, adapting its approach to fit different business models and market conditions. The firm is also registered as an investment adviser with relevant regulators.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/90071afc-7217-4d6f-859e-04a581743e21.png', TRUE, 'Small company', NULL, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-17T00:00:00+00:00', '90071afc-7217-4d6f-859e-04a581743e21') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('T-minus', 'The Performants Group Limited (Trading as T-minus)', 'https://wearetminus.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/wearetminus', 'T–minus is a UK-based leadership development company that focuses on high-growth programs, assessments, strategic offsites, and coaching. The company aims to help leaders adapt and thrive in times of disruption and change. T–minus is known as "The Change Makers" and features a team of experts, including psychologists, neuroscientists, and coaches, who work together to create tailored solutions for startups and corporates.The company offers a variety of leadership development programs designed for executives and senior leaders. These include bespoke programs that blend Agile methodologies with entrepreneurship and coaching, as well as specialized offerings like the "Innovation Leader" program, which enhances strategic innovation projects. T–minus emphasizes rapid experimentation and customer-led innovation, helping leaders build resilience and adaptability in their organizations. The company has successfully partnered with over 100 organizations, including notable clients such as Disney, Unilever, and ASOS, delivering impactful results and fostering lasting change.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ab0ae670-db6b-49b8-8fda-75ee689501f0.png', TRUE, NULL, NULL, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-10T00:00:00+00:00', 'ab0ae670-db6b-49b8-8fda-75ee689501f0') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('The Pace Centre', 'The Pace Centre Limited', 'https://thepacecentre.org', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/the-pace-centre-limited', 'Pace is a charity which delivers specialist education and therapies to babies, children and young people with neurodisabilities like cerebral palsy from 0-18 years of age. 

Our services include

 - Early intervention and support for children 0-4 years and their families

 - School, 4-16 years delivering a tailored integrated curriculum through our unique blended approach

 - Outreach, working with children and young people within other educational settings or dual placements', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/80d2b1b1-2fa4-4c2c-a1da-d7323deb5349.png', TRUE, 'Medium-sized company', NULL, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-09T00:00:00+00:00', '80d2b1b1-2fa4-4c2c-a1da-d7323deb5349') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('The Race Media', 'The Race Media', 'https://theracemedialtd.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/the-race-media-ltd', 'The Race Media is the largest independent motorsport media company, established in February 2020. Based in Newcastle Upon Tyne, England, it operates as a digital-only channel and was acquired by RAFA Media in October 2024. The company is dedicated to democratizing access to motorsports by creating high-quality, authentic content for both dedicated fans and newcomers.

The Race Media encompasses several content brands, including its flagship channel, The Race, which produces videos, podcasts, and editorial content. It also includes WTF1, which engages a young audience, and the Driver Database, a resource for motorsport information. Additionally, WTF Talent is an influencer agency focused on motorsport, and The Race Media Studios offers channel management solutions. The company reaches a vast audience through various channels, including social media and live events, and has seen significant growth, particularly with the rising popularity of Formula 1 in the United States.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/2e9b7bc6-d849-4c47-b6b2-ce5749afe361.png', TRUE, 'Medium-sized company', NULL, NULL, FALSE, '2026-03-05T00:00:00+00:00', '2e9b7bc6-d849-4c47-b6b2-ce5749afe361') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Thema', 'THEMA AI LIMITED', 'https://thema.ai', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/thema-ai', 'Most tools answer: "What companies look similar?" 

Thema answers: "Where should we expand, where should we originate, and where does risk sit across our portfolio?"

We continuously map market structure, adjacencies, and competitive dynamics – giving private equity teams a living view of the global economy built for high-stakes decisions.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e505b50e-ba58-4724-a755-78a8f2d788f7.png', TRUE, 'Small company', NULL, NULL, FALSE, '2026-02-25T00:00:00+00:00', 'e505b50e-ba58-4724-a755-78a8f2d788f7') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Thomas Carroll', 'Thomas, Carroll (Brokers) Ltd', 'https://www.thomascarroll.co.uk', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/thomas-carroll', 'Thomas Carroll Group plc is a prominent independent insurance broker and financial services provider based in the UK. Founded in 1972 and headquartered in Caerphilly, Wales, the company has over 50 years of experience in delivering business and personal insurance broking, employee benefits, wealth management, health and safety consultancy, and employment law services. As an employee-owned business, all 181 employees are co-owners, fostering a culture of engagement and performance.

The company offers a wide range of services, including tailored business insurance solutions, personal insurance coverage, employee benefits programs, and comprehensive wealth management advice. It also provides health and safety consultancy and employment law services to support compliance and dispute resolution. Thomas Carroll Group has received recognition for its high standards, including accolades such as "Insurance Brokers of the Decade" at the 2014 British Insurance Awards. With additional offices in various UK locations, the company emphasizes strong client relationships and community involvement through charitable initiatives.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/92b20dbe-ffe4-4019-b6ba-11501c5e9acc.png', TRUE, 'Medium-sized company', NULL, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-09T00:00:00+00:00', '92b20dbe-ffe4-4019-b6ba-11501c5e9acc') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Track24', 'Track 24 Limited', 'https://www.track24.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/track24', 'Track24 is a London-based security and investigations company founded in 2004. It specializes in location intelligence technology aimed at enhancing duty of care, operations management, communications, and risk mitigation. With around 37 employees and an annual revenue of $7 million as of 2025, Track24 operates in 35 countries and has offices in Dubai, Sharjah, and London.

The company’s flagship product, AtlasNXT, is a customizable SaaS platform designed to protect high-value assets, including employees and sites. It features advanced capabilities such as 3D precision communications, smart geofencing, real-time analysis, and automated alerts. Track24 emphasizes privacy and compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and ISO 31030:2021. The company also offers onboarding, training, and 24/7 support, ensuring operational resilience and effective risk management for its clients, which include large multinationals, government agencies, and NGOs.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/58fbcdfb-594d-4a63-a85e-3081c8e83509.png', TRUE, 'Small company', NULL, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-16T00:00:00+00:00', '58fbcdfb-594d-4a63-a85e-3081c8e83509') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('TransPerfect', 'TRANSPERFECT TRANSLATIONS LIMITED', 'https://www.transperfect.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/transperfect', 'TransPerfect is the largest privately held provider of language and business services, founded in 1992 by Phil Shawe and Liz Elting. The company has grown significantly, achieving revenues of $1.16 billion in 2022 and operating offices in over 100 cities worldwide with a workforce exceeding 7,500 employees.TransPerfect offers a wide range of services, including translation and localization for software, websites, and technical documentation. They provide live translation services and electronic discovery services, as well as component content management systems for multilingual documentation. The company also specializes in technical audiovisual services, operating over 90 recording rooms and eight theatrical rooms globally. TransPerfect has expanded through strategic acquisitions, enhancing its capabilities in various sectors, and is recognized as a leader in the language services industry, serving prominent organizations across multiple fields.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 62, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/e9ec9ade-ef3d-43f1-8bc1-2c09ff40b16f.png', TRUE, NULL, 8, NULL, FALSE, NULL, 'e9ec9ade-ef3d-43f1-8bc1-2c09ff40b16f') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Transmission', 'Transmission Production Limited', 'https://www.wearetransmission.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/transmission-productions-ltd', 'PASSION.

It''s what sets us apart. And you from your competition.

That''s why we never settle. And nor should you.

We take inspiration from your aspirations. Creating and making TV, Film and Audio campaigns that move people.

Stirring emotions.  Spurring desire.  Provoking response.

This is what we call
PASSION IN MOTION

Because passion is infectious and we''re experts in transmission.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/67baa5fa-8804-4c98-9a62-62e9c1965755.png', TRUE, 'Small company', NULL, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-16T00:00:00+00:00', '67baa5fa-8804-4c98-9a62-62e9c1965755') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Trium Capital', 'Trium Capital LLP', 'https://trium-capital.com', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/trium-capital-llp', 'Trium Capital is a London-based asset manager that specializes in liquid alternatives. The firm focuses on launching and accelerating funds for portfolio managers who aim to establish their own funds but may lack experience in business management or risk control. Trium Capital provides institutional-level risk management, operational support, and strategy refinement to help these managers create investable strategies that meet high standards.

As a hedge fund manager, Trium Capital oversees discretionary assets under management for 25 clients. The firm emphasizes responsible investment and ESG factors to achieve optimal risk-adjusted returns. It promotes a collaborative approach, working closely with portfolio managers to refine their strategies and ensure consistency. Trium Capital values diversity of thought, integrity, and long-term partnerships, incentivizing managers through personal capital commitments and performance-based structures.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/ed5377b8-4de1-4a7e-ad1d-2d6bab0d2141.png', TRUE, 'Medium-sized company', NULL, NULL, TRUE, '2026-03-18T00:00:00+00:00', 'ed5377b8-4de1-4a7e-ad1d-2d6bab0d2141') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Tuza', 'Statement Technologies Limited T/A Tuza', 'https://www.tuza.ai', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/trytuza', 'Tuza is a London-based fintech company founded in 2023 by Ed Hardy and Olivia Stannah. It operates a free price comparison platform specifically designed for small and medium-sized businesses (SMBs) in the UK, helping them compare card payment processing rates from top providers like Worldpay, Barclaycard, and Revolut. The platform allows users to complete comparisons quickly, often in under two minutes, and aims to optimize payment costs by eliminating hidden fees and complex pricing structures.

In addition to its comparison tool, Tuza is developing a digital exchange for payments in collaboration with major banks. This initiative focuses on digitizing onboarding and pricing processes to reduce costs associated with manual risk pricing. The company has secured £4 million in seed funding to support its growth and enhance its technical capabilities. Tuza targets approximately 1.5 million SMBs across various sectors, including retail and e-commerce, promoting pricing fairness and efficient provider switching.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/083c2af7-b0e7-44cb-9c3a-04ac4c91d902.png', TRUE, 'Small company', NULL, NULL, FALSE, '2026-02-25T00:00:00+00:00', '083c2af7-b0e7-44cb-9c3a-04ac4c91d902') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('UIC Digital', 'UIC Digital Ltd', 'https://uicdigital.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/uic-digital', 'UIC Digital is a creative engineering company based in the UK, founded in 2008. It specializes in developing high-quality digital products across web, mobile, and OTT platforms, with a strong emphasis on user experience. Headquartered in London, UIC Digital also has offices in New York and Budapest, employing a team of 60-100 experts in various roles, including software development, product strategy, and creative design.

The company offers a comprehensive range of services, including digital strategy and consulting, UX/UI design, full-stack development, and project delivery. UIC Digital is committed to delivering exceptional user experiences and works with notable clients such as BBC, UEFA, FIFA, NBC, and Diageo. With a focus on collaboration and quality, UIC Digital fosters a positive workplace culture and engages in community activities like mentoring and volunteering.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/5cca094b-43b0-4c59-a276-2aabb9f9900a.png', TRUE, 'Medium-sized company', NULL, NULL, FALSE, '2026-03-06T00:00:00+00:00', '5cca094b-43b0-4c59-a276-2aabb9f9900a') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('UNIQLO', 'Uniqlo Europe Ltd', 'https://www.uniqlo.com/uk/en/information', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/uniqlo', 'UNIQLO is a global Japanese clothing brand founded in 1949 in Yamaguchi, Japan. Originally a textiles manufacturer, it has grown into a leading retailer of casual wear, operating over 1,000 stores worldwide as part of the Fast Retailing Group. UNIQLO focuses on high-quality, innovative casual clothing designed for comfort and longevity, guided by its LifeWear philosophy, which emphasizes the integration of art, science, functionality, and sustainability.

The company offers a wide range of casual apparel for women, men, and children, featuring advanced fabrics like HEATTECH for warmth, AIRism for breathability, and BLOCKTECH for water resistance. UNIQLO is committed to sustainability, promoting initiatives such as a global All-Product Recycling program that supports refugees and displaced individuals. With a strong presence in North America, Europe, and Asia, UNIQLO continues to expand its retail model through both physical stores and online sales, while collaborating with global partners to ensure quality and sustainable production practices.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 6, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/acdb154b-5e95-474e-ad2c-234a71e98937.png', TRUE, 'Very large company', 16, NULL, FALSE, NULL, 'acdb154b-5e95-474e-ad2c-234a71e98937') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO companies (trading_name, companies_house_name, url, url_linkedin, description, policy, open_to_sponsorship, active_jobs_count, url_favicon, licensed_sponsor, estimated_num_employees_label, cos_used_count_2025, sponsored_employees_count, show_recently_added_badge, added_to_register, favicon_id) VALUES ('Ulla', 'ULLA TECHNOLOGY LTD', 'https://ulla.bot', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/ulla-technology', 'Ulla Technology is an AI-driven Family of products to monitor and improve business communication and performance. 
Our tools help teams understand how they collaborate, make decisions, share information and progress - in real meetings, real conversations, and real workflows.
From automated meeting notes to engagement analytics and personality insights, Ulla turns everyday communication into clarity, structure and measurable outcomes.

Our Products
• Ulla® Notetaker - Simple and secure AI-driven notetaker that instantly transforms discussions into clear summaries and actionable points, allowing teams to focus on priorities.
• Ulla® HR Engagement - metrics to track participation, clarity, tone, collaboration patterns, burnout signals and team communication health.
• Ulla® HR Personality Assessment - like Big Five, MBTI-style and behavioural insights based on natural conversation, not surveys.
• Ulla® Interview - AI-powered solutions for voice interviews and surveys.

Where Ulla is used
Ulla Family products can be combined or used individually across industries - recruitment, HR, sales, public sector, legal, education, IT, and corporate teams of any size.

Our Approach
We believe organisations don''t need to control people - they need to understand the patterns. Ulla reveals those patterns, improves communication quality and helps teams work healthier and perform better.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/73078b26-1f6c-479d-9e1c-c00d190fa320.png', TRUE, 'Small company', NULL, NULL, FALSE, '2026-02-23T00:00:00+00:00', '73078b26-1f6c-479d-9e1c-c00d190fa320') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
