Across residential, commercial and freehold assets, our approach remains consistent. We support landlords, leaseholders and residents through clear oversight, structured processes and reliable operational delivery.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/0ee83803-3ef6-45ba-a0d5-7435d55d7a77.png', TRUE, 'Small company', NULL, NULL, FALSE, '2026-02-23T00:00:00+00:00', '0ee83803-3ef6-45ba-a0d5-7435d55d7a77') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
