The company''s flagship product, Xfuze, is an AI-powered composable integration and data management platform delivered as a cloud-native SaaS solution. Xfuze connects systems in real-time, unifies data into a single view, and provides actionable insights and advanced analytics. Xiatech also offers consultancy services in IT strategy, omni-channel eCommerce, project delivery, enterprise architecture, microservices, and big data. The company partners with global digital leaders, particularly in retail, to drive transformation and performance.', 'The company is a licensed sponsor.', 4, 0, 'https://xhtezeeaeqjfdhrkltox.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/company_icons/b7ca22e3-92ff-41d9-8ed9-20c4ad7a08bf.png', TRUE, 'Medium-sized company', NULL, NULL, FALSE, '2026-02-24T00:00:00+00:00', 'b7ca22e3-92ff-41d9-8ed9-20c4ad7a08bf') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
